1)add the flutter_native_splash package
flutter pub add flutter_native_splash
2)on cr√©e un fichier splash.yaml(au niveau du main)
flutter_native_splash:
  color: "#FFFFFF"
  color_dark: "#000000"
  image: assets/logos/t-store-splash-logo-black.png
  image_dark: assets/logos/t-store-splash-logo-white.png

  android_12:
    color: "#FFFFFF"
    color_dark: "#000000"
    image: assets/logos/t-store-splash-logo-black.png
    image_dark: assets/logos/t-store-splash-logo-white.png


  web: false

3)flutter pub run flutter_native_splash:create --path=splash.yaml


-------- remove splash screen ------
4)flutter pub run flutter_native_splash:remove